### Phase 2: Draw Call and Rendering

**Q2.1: Draw call optimization**

| Metric | Current | Target | Strategy |
|--------|---------|--------|----------|
| Draw calls per frame | | < 1000 (mobile) | Batching, instancing |
| State changes | | Minimize | Sort by state |
| Overdraw | | Profile | Occlusion, culling |
| Shader complexity | | Profile | LOD, simplification |

**Q2.2: Rendering pipeline**

- [ ] Batching/instancing used where applicable
- [ ] Materials sorted to reduce state changes
- [ ] Frustum culling implemented
- [ ] Occlusion culling considered for complex scenes
- [ ] LOD system reduces draw cost at distance

