### Phase 4: GC Pressure (Managed Runtimes)

**Q4.1: Garbage collection impact**

| Concern | Current | Target | Mitigation |
|---------|---------|--------|------------|
| Allocations per frame | | Zero in hot path | |
| GC frequency | | Rare during gameplay | |
| GC pause duration | | < 1ms | |
| Boxing in hot path | | None | |

**Q4.2: GC avoidance checklist**

- [ ] No string concatenation in update loop
- [ ] No LINQ/iterator allocations in hot path
- [ ] Structs used where value semantics suffice
- [ ] Collections pre-allocated or pooled
- [ ] Lambda captures avoid allocation (static, cached)

