### Phase 6: GPU vs CPU Bound

**Q6.1: Bottleneck identification**

| Scenario | CPU Time | GPU Time | Bound | Action |
|----------|----------|----------|-------|--------|
| Typical gameplay | | | | |
| Worst case | | | | |
| Menu/UI | | | | |

**Q6.2: Optimization priority**

When CPU-bound: Reduce draw calls, simplify logic, parallelize systems.
When GPU-bound: Reduce pixel cost, simplify shaders, lower resolution/quality.

- [ ] Bottleneck clearly identified with profiling data
- [ ] Optimization strategy matches bottleneck type
- [ ] No premature optimization (profile first)

